THE FULL DEETS
Did you know that only 13% of plastic is recycled in the EU, compared to 85% of all PET bottles and aluminium cans?! We believe the huge difference is due to the existing bottle deposit schemes. I mean, who doesn't like to get rewarded for recycling, right?!

Now we're taking that same approach with takeaway packaging. It's highly likely that the disposable container you tossed recently was either non recyclable, or would be pulverised, never to see the light of day again.

We're fed up with corporations and legislation lagging behind, so we've decided to fast track takeaway packaging recycling into the circular world. Part of that commitment means that we supply environmentally friendly packaging to restaurants that can actually be recycled multiple times once sorted.

But here's the thing, though - that's only one half of the equation! To really close the gap, we 100% need your help to get more takeaway packaging back into the circular loop. Together, we can make the change we want to see in the world!

SORTING & RECYCLING - HOW & WHERE
Once you're done with your tasty meal, it's important to both remove any food waste and separate plastic from paper (where possible). By doing these two things, you provide the best chance for the packaging to be accepted for recycling!

HOW DO I ACTUALLY PAY FOR THINGS WITH MY CREDITS?!
